1
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,079
Sigh...

2
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,959
Are you leaving?

3
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,319
Your student is tired.

4
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,200
I want to go open a private school.

5
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,599
Daliang currently

6
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,640
still has no emperor.

7
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:24,959
Right now,

8
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,239
we urgently need someone to keep searching for a suitable prince to take the throne.

9
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,359
Forgive my incompetence.

10
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,959
I'm afraid I can't shoulder such a heavy responsibility.

11
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,319
Qi Zhi,

12
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:40,000
you're letting the Crown Prince down.

13
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,120
Only by

14
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,640
finding a suitable prince,

15
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,319
putting him on the throne,

16
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:45,400
and having him rule Daliang,

17
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,239
can we resolve what's

18
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:48,840
most urgent right now.

19
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:52,120
It's also the Crown Prince's

20
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,400
dying wish.

21
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:55,680
Of course,

22
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,959
you have the right to choose.

23
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,719
If you want to leave,

24
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,519
I won't force you.

25
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:12,439
Ouyang Yan.

26
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,560
What brings you here?

27
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,879
What?

28
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,680
I'm not allowed to come back?

29
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:18,400
Ah.

30
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,360
No, no, no.

31
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,560
I'm just a bit surprised.

32
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:22,840
You just got here, and I'm about to leave.

33
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:24,439
Hey.

34
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,400
How long are you staying?

35
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,719
Maybe

36
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,919
I'll still get to see you when I get back.

37
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:28,000
Me?

38
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,680
I'm leaving right away.

39
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,439
In such a hurry?

40
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,840
Sigh.

41
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,719
Didn't I hear

42
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,319
the palace sent another Special Envoy

43
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:39,240
to search for the heir to the throne?

44
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,479
So I have to set out immediately

45
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,800
to leave with him.

46
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,319
Hey.

47
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,039
So you still want to be Empress?

48
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,680
Don't bring up sore subjects.

49
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,199
I'm off.

50
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,639
The Crown Prince just wanted a place

51
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,919
to draw his comics in peace.

52
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,479
Such a simple wish.

53
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,599
Why wouldn't heaven grant it?

54
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:05,560
Sigh.

55
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,400
All we can do now

56
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,680
is try our best to fulfill his dying wish.

57
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,120
As for Huahua,

58
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:18,479
well,

59
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:19,560
every chicken has its own fate.

60
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:20,800
I mean,

61
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,120
for a chicken,

62
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,080
living two years

63
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:24,479
is already a long life.

64
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,000
Hey.

65
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,280
Weren't you all hopeless about life before?

66
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,719
No.

67
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,560
I feel hopeless every single day.

68
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:37,520
I can't believe I went soft on you.

69
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,439
I must've been bewitched.

70
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,560
Sigh.

71
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:43,080
Fine, get going.

72
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,680
Find the heir to the throne,

73
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,240
give him the late emperor's jade pendant,

74
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,919
and hurry up and become Empress.

75
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,560
Hey.

76
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,479
That jade pendant...

77
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:52,560
didn't I already smash it to pieces?

78
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,360
Oh.

79
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,280
Here's the thing.

80
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,000
As emperor,

81
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,360
the late emperor in his lifetime

82
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:59,159
wore many jade pendants.

83
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,879
Why didn't you say so sooner?

84
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:03,479
And here I was feeling

85
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,599
guilty about it for quite a while.

86
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,919
Well, you never asked.

87
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,400
You're awful.

88
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,800
Don't you know to respect your elders?

89
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,680
Speak.

90
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,800
Who sent you to rescue me?

91
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,480
Lord Li.

92
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,399
Young prince.

93
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,120
It's been a while.

94
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,959
Eunuch, you've grown

95
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,920
quite a bit more haggard lately.

96
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,680
Wait, no.

97
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,959
What I want is simple.

98
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,839
Eunuch, you're resourceful

99
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:49,199
and powerful at court.

100
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,360
If you and I joined forces,

101
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,680
we'd surely make a comeback.

102
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,199
Who are you?

103
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:56,639
Ah.

104
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:58,040
I didn't mean anything by it.

105
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,399
I just wanted to say,

106
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,079
even if we cooperate,

107
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,639
I still need to know who you are.

108
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,920
Oh, it's you.

109
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:25,879
All the vendors are women.

110
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:28,360
What are these women all doing?

111
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,759
Hey.

112
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,439
"Code for Men."

113
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:41,319
Rongcheng seems to be a place where women rule.

114
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,079
You mean...

115
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,600
Women are in charge?

116
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,560
Mm.

117
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,879
It says here

118
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:46,920
that men must obey

119
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,160
the Three Obediences and Four Virtues,

120
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,120
and serve their in-laws.

121
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,199
Then aren't women supposed to

122
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,959
earn money to support the family

123
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:52,800
and defend the nation?

124
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:53,439
Ha.

125
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,480
No way.

126
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,439
Before marriage, obey the mother;

127
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,519
once married, obey the wife;

128
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,759
when the wife dies, obey the daughter.

129
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,279
It really is true.

130
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,879
The women in this city,

131
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:07,160
why are they all like tigresses?

132
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:09,240
As if you weren't a tigress yourself.

133
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,399
Hey!

134
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:11,879
How dare you say that to me?

135
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,079
Oh!

136
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,000
Hey!

137
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:14,920
As a husband,

138
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,879
how dare you speak rudely to your own wife?

139
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:17,920
You want a beating?

140
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,040
Hahaha.

141
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,839
You've misunderstood.

142
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:21,319
It's a misunderstanding.

143
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:21,480
We're...

144
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,480
Hey, hey, hey!

145
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,240
Talk all you want,

146
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,600
but why are you hitting me?

147
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:24,959
Hmph!

148
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:27,319
Looks like he's been spoiled rotten.

149
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,240
Hey, hey, hey!

150
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,040
Forget it, forget it.

151
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,160
Just let it go.

152
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,199
Don't, don't hit him!

153
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:32,879
Oh!

154
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,920
Why are you such a coward?

155
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,480
She's bullying you right to your face.

156
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,519
No way.

157
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,000
Hey!

158
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,399
Let's settle this!

159
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:38,839
Don't make trouble.

160
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,199
I'm not going.

161
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,079
My lady!

162
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,519
My lady, please stop hitting me!

163
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,600
You good-for-nothing!

164
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,199
Ugly and a glutton,

165
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,360
and you can't even do any work!

166
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,480
You won't let me divorce you?

167
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,360
If I don't, what am I keeping you around for?

168
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:52,519
My lady!

169
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:52,879
Get lost!

170
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,040
Don't divorce me, my lady!

171
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,439
This is going too far!

172
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,480
Madam Official,

173
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,759
please show some mercy!

174
00:06:59,079 --> 00:06:59,879
Madam Officials,

175
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,399
Prince of Rong,

176
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,399
why are you beating him

177
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,959
like this?

178
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:09,839
This man caused a public disturbance.

179
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,959
Rather than handing him to the authorities,

180
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,439
it'd be better to leave him to us,

181
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,079
the Husbands' Association, to handle.

182
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,000
That would be more appropriate.

183
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,839
Madam Officials, both of you,

184
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,480
what do you think?

185
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,600
The Prince of Rong makes a fair point.

186
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,240
Then we'll trouble you with it.

187
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,920
After you, everyone.

188
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,920
Get out of here, you!

189
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,759
From now on,

190
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:41,480
listen to your wife more

191
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,560
and try to please her.

192
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,720
Thank you, Prince of Rong.

193
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,000
Thank you, Prince of Rong.

194
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,720
Off you go.

195
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,560
My lady!

196
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,639
Wait for me!

197
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,279
My lady!

198
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,639
Prince of Rong, please wait!

199
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:57,879
And you two are...?

200
00:07:58,839 --> 00:07:59,639
Oh.

201
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:01,759
We're Special Envoys sent by the palace.

202
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,920
We're passing through Rongcheng,

203
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,279
and we see its people live in peace and prosperity.

204
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,279
Surely thanks to your wise rule, Prince of Rong.

205
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,199
We've come to invite you back to the palace

206
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,240
to become emperor.

207
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,600
I

208
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,839
have been close with the Crown Prince since childhood.

209
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,360
I never imagined

210
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,240
I'd miss seeing him one last time.

211
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,360
Life is unpredictable.

212
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,040
We wonder, Your Highness,

213
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,639
we wonder, Your Highness,

214
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:29,120
about returning to the capital to take the throne—

215
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,279
what do you think?

216
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,320
I'm not capable enough.

217
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,639
I'm afraid the Special Envoys this time

218
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,360
will have to find someone else.

219
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,960
Another one refusing?

220
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,799
Your Highness,

221
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,799
since

222
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:44,120
you say you and the Crown Prince were close since childhood,

223
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:46,440
then you should fulfill his final wish.

224
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:47,919
That's true.

225
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,879
If the Crown Prince knew in the afterlife

226
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,399
that the Prince of Rong took the throne,

227
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,360
surely

228
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,759
he'd rest in peace.

229
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:55,960
It's not that I'm

230
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,879
deliberately refusing.

231
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:57,960
I'm just afraid

232
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,600
that my

233
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,720
wife,

234
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,360
she...

235
00:09:00,879 --> 00:09:02,039
won't let me go.

236
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:03,960
That's easy.

237
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,200
Just divorce her,

238
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,679
and make me your empress.

239
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,559
Hey!

240
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:11,440
What?

241
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,519
Don't tell me

242
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:16,480
this princess is no match for your wife?

243
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,320
No, no, no.

244
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:20,000
How would I ever look down on the princess?

245
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,919
It's just that you two don't know—

246
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,960
right now, here in Rongcheng...

247
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,039
Princess Consort of Rong arrives!

248
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,759
Who are they?

249
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,159
My dear,

250
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,360
these two

251
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,759
are Special Envoys from the capital.

252
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,639
What's their business?

253
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,200
Well...

254
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:54,519
It's like this.

255
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,039
The reason we came...

256
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:55,720
How dare you!

257
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,039
In the Princess Consort's presence,

258
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,240
no man has the right to speak.

259
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,399
Right.

260
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,159
Isn't that so?

261
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,120
Then I'll speak.

262
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,759
This time we

263
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,799
came to bring the Prince of Rong back to the capital

264
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,360
to inherit the throne.

265
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:08,879
Hey, hey, hey!

266
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:09,879
I don't agree.

267
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,759
What gives you the right?

268
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,120
Hey!

269
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,440
You two, leave first.

270
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,440
I'll see you out.

271
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,000
After you, please.

272
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,559
See you later!

273
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,159
Go ahead.

274
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,120
What?

275
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:39,039
You can't divorce her.

276
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,120
Exactly.

277
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,120
So...

278
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,879
Unless Bandeng divorces me,

279
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,399
there's simply no way

280
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:48,120
I can leave Rongcheng.

281
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:50,480
Unless...

282
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,519
What divorces you?

283
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,000
Bandeng, of course.

284
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,639
What "Bandeng"?

285
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:57,919
Oh.

286
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,000
Uh...

287
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,320
My beloved wife's pet name

288
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:01,200
is Bandeng.

289
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,600
Are you called Biandan, then?

290
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,039
What a peculiar name!

291
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,000
I...

292
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:06,559
don't have

293
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,080
a pet name.

294
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,759
A woman divorcing her husband?

295
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,879
Such things actually happen in Daliang?

296
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,360
Well, here it is, isn't it?

297
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,480
I don't care if she's Biandan, Bandeng, or a table.

298
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,879
I don't care if she's Biandan, Bandeng, or a table.

299
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,200
If she won't divorce you,

300
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:21,360
I'll beat her until she does.

301
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,720
Sister,

302
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,799
you saw that whole spectacle just now.

303
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,679
They just had numbers, that's all.

304
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:28,039
Just a few lackeys.

305
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,960
Are you looking down on me?

306
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,480
Hey, you...

307
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,279
Actually,

308
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,480
this isn't really Bandeng's fault.

309
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:38,960
She had a tragic childhood.

310
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,879
Her mother

311
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,519
used to be a singing girl at a brothel.

312
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:45,720
From childhood,

313
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,679
she watched her mother

314
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,320
being oppressed,

315
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,200
humiliated by men,

316
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:54,639
and eventually beaten to death.

317
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:56,080
That's why Bandeng

318
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:58,879
came to despise men so deeply.

319
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:02,200
She looks so haughty,

320
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,759
but has such a story behind her.

321
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:06,320
How pitiful.

322
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,159
But still,

323
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,679
even so,

324
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,720
she can't just go around

325
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,919
oppressing others

326
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:13,519
to get back at the world.

327
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:14,279
Exactly.

328
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,279
We still need to find a way

329
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,399
to make her divorce you.

330
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,799
I do have one idea,

331
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,039
the question is whether you two dare.

332
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,000
What idea?

333
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,759
Tell us, tell us!

334
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,120
Bandeng recently

335
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:26,960
took a 28th concubine.

336
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,360
Let me out!

337
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,399
You two

338
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:31,120
can start with him.

339
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:31,519
Hey!

340
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,440
What are you doing?

341
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,399
Even as a concubine, I won't be the 28th!

342
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,679
I refuse!

343
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,399
How dare you!

344
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:43,679
Hey!

345
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:45,720
You think I'm crazy?

346
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,559
If I let him out,

347
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,679
he'll become emperor.

348
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:50,039
Am I a fool?

349
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:52,240
Help us escape,

350
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:54,120
and we'll help you escape too.

351
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:57,039
Have you ever told me the truth?

352
00:12:57,879 --> 00:12:59,399
If you don't help us,

353
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:03,159
I'll make sure you never climb a wall again.

354
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:05,440
You wouldn't dare!

355
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,000
Try me and see.

356
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:09,879
So stubbornly blind, are you?

357
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,399
Let's do it.

358
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,559
How long has it been since you ate?

359
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,639
Five days.

360
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:25,360
Give me five more.

361
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:26,480
Five?

362
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,320
Every time I try to escape,

363
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,679
they make me skip a meal.

364
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,759
That's only one meal, though.

365
00:13:34,879 --> 00:13:36,240
I've run nine times.

366
00:13:39,679 --> 00:13:40,519
I want to eat.

367
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:41,399
Well then,

368
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,840
help us out

369
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,320
and handle Bandeng for us.

370
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,159
Otherwise...

371
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:47,320
Hey!

372
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:49,440
It's not that I don't want to help.

373
00:13:49,679 --> 00:13:51,279
I truly can't help you.

374
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,200
Bandeng stopped coming to me ages ago.

375
00:13:53,799 --> 00:13:55,120
Don't try to be clever with me.

376
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:57,360
Why would I lie to you?

377
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,360
If I were really her favorite,

378
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,840
would I be starving like this?

379
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:04,200
The brothel's top star is Bandeng's new sweetheart.

380
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:05,840
Yes, yes, yes.

381
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,600
I heard recently

382
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,360
a new one arrived at the brothel.

383
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,120
Some top-ranked star.

384
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,399
Yes, yes, yes.

385
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,679
It's that one called Zhi Hua.

386
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:15,919
Every word I said is true.

387
00:14:15,919 --> 00:14:17,200
Just let me eat already.

388
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,399
Hmph.

389
00:14:21,039 --> 00:14:23,120
Looks like we have to visit the brothel.

390
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,320
Hey!

391
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:29,240
You promised to set me free!

392
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:32,559
Don't you want to be Emperor?

393
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:33,600
Right.

394
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:37,080
When Heaven entrusts a great mission,

395
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,000
it must first

396
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,600
torment one's spirit,

397
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,879
strain one's muscles,

398
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:43,200
and starve one's body.

399
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:45,519
Hey!

400
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,679
Take good care of him.

401
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,879
My lady, just call me if you need anything.

402
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:56,639
Let me know if anything's amiss.

403
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,440
Oh my!

404
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,320
Dear guest,

405
00:15:00,799 --> 00:15:01,600
where did you

406
00:15:01,759 --> 00:15:03,440
buy this cute little husband?

407
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,799
He's so handsome.

408
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:05,480
Hey, hey, hey!

409
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:08,440
How dare you touch a customer's property?

410
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:10,639
Is this how you run a business?

411
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:11,440
Oh my.

412
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:13,320
What are you saying?

413
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:13,960
Look,

414
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,840
we're all here for some fun.

415
00:15:15,879 --> 00:15:16,679
How about

416
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:17,919
you hand him over to me?

417
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,360
I'll look after him for you.

418
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,000
Hey.

419
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,399
No, no, no.

420
00:15:21,759 --> 00:15:23,440
Go cool off somewhere else.

421
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:24,879
Ugh.

422
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:27,240
How shameless can you be?

423
00:15:28,799 --> 00:15:29,600
What did you say?

424
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:41,559
Where's Zhi Hua?

425
00:15:41,679 --> 00:15:42,440
We want to see Zhi Hua!

426
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:47,240
The man Bandeng pines for so much,

427
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:50,600
I want to see just how handsome he is.

428
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:51,399
How vulgar.

429
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:52,639
Everyone, don't rush.

430
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:53,440
Zhi Hua

431
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,120
will be out shortly.

432
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,799
Heh heh heh.

433
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,159
Wow.

434
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,240
Bandeng,

435
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,679
your taste is that wild?

436
00:16:06,639 --> 00:16:07,440
Oh my.

437
00:16:07,679 --> 00:16:08,480
Dear guests,

438
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,639
I'm terribly sorry.

439
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:12,159
Today, Zhi Hua and the Baicao Pavilion

440
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:14,120
have been booked by a distinguished guest.

441
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:16,960
Please, everyone,

442
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,279
come back tomorrow.

443
00:16:18,279 --> 00:16:19,000
Ha ha ha.

444
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:22,600
My apologies, everyone.

445
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,360
So sorry.

446
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:23,840
I'm sorry.

447
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,799
My apologies.

448
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:31,639
What's going on?

449
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:34,679
Baicao Pavilion's been booked by a noble today.

450
00:16:34,879 --> 00:16:35,679
Clear the place.

451
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,120
Get in there.

452
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:47,840
Ouch!

453
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:50,679
You violent woman!

454
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,799
I thought I was dead at the time.

455
00:17:02,039 --> 00:17:03,480
But General Li was thorough.

456
00:17:03,639 --> 00:17:05,400
He realized I'd only passed out.

457
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,000
So he secretly smuggled me out of the palace.

458
00:17:07,039 --> 00:17:09,240
I was bedridden for ages before I recovered.

459
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,000
Once I got better,

460
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,720
I wanted to hurry back to the palace.

461
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,079
But General Li said

462
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,440
the palace wasn't safe yet,

463
00:17:15,799 --> 00:17:17,680
and told me to lie low and wait it out.

464
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,799
But I couldn't stand it.

465
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,119
I figured I'd go out and wander a bit,

466
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:23,559
and that's how I ended up in Rongcheng.

467
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,519
Who would've thought,

468
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,279
the moment I arrived, I got dragged to Baicao Pavilion.

469
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:28,440
Well, that's great.

470
00:17:28,559 --> 00:17:29,759
Pack up your things quickly.

471
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:30,559
Let's get out of here.

472
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:30,880
Come on.

473
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:32,720
Go where?

474
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,039
Are you stupid?

475
00:17:34,039 --> 00:17:35,720
To rescue you and escape, of course!

476
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,240
Don't worry.

477
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,519
Those people outside

478
00:17:38,839 --> 00:17:40,000
are no match for me.

479
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:41,559
I'm not running away.

480
00:17:42,119 --> 00:17:43,160
You know what?

481
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:45,799
Never have so many people loved my comics.

482
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,440
They don't care about my status,

483
00:17:47,519 --> 00:17:48,799
nor do they care who I am.

484
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,839
They're my true, genuine fans.

485
00:17:51,279 --> 00:17:52,880
This is the life I've been chasing!

486
00:17:53,039 --> 00:17:54,240
The life you're chasing?

487
00:17:54,559 --> 00:17:56,079
Do you have any idea how many lives

488
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:57,400
have been ruined for the life you're chasing?

489
00:17:57,519 --> 00:17:59,240
Why didn't you tell us sooner you were alive?

490
00:18:03,359 --> 00:18:04,119
Well,

491
00:18:04,119 --> 00:18:05,359
General Li told me

492
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,759
not to let too many people know.

493
00:18:09,599 --> 00:18:10,400
What's this?

494
00:18:12,279 --> 00:18:13,640
Not running today?

495
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,400
Done causing trouble?

496
00:18:17,359 --> 00:18:17,960
My lady,

497
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,640
Twenty-Eighth Brother is too young,

498
00:18:21,039 --> 00:18:22,279
pampered since childhood.

499
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,160
Him not wanting to be a concubine

500
00:18:24,839 --> 00:18:25,960
is perfectly normal.

501
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:27,960
Speak up.

502
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,720
What brings you to me today?

503
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,039
My lady,

504
00:18:33,519 --> 00:18:35,319
I was wrong about what happened earlier.

505
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:36,960
This cup of tea,

506
00:18:37,319 --> 00:18:37,960
this cup of tea,

507
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,799
is my apology to you.

508
00:18:47,279 --> 00:18:48,240
So well-behaved today, are we?

509
00:18:53,319 --> 00:18:54,119
How about

510
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,799
you drink this cup of tea for me?

511
00:18:59,359 --> 00:19:00,160
No, no, no.

512
00:19:00,319 --> 00:19:01,079
My lady,

513
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:02,559
this tea was specially prepared for you.

514
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:03,880
Drink it and I'll forgive you.

515
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,279
Drink it!

516
00:19:08,039 --> 00:19:08,839
Drink it!

517
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,599
Still hasn't learned his lesson.

518
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,440
Yes, yes, yes.

519
00:19:26,519 --> 00:19:27,680
Starve him for another three days.

520
00:19:30,799 --> 00:19:32,039
Why are you walking so fast?

521
00:19:33,519 --> 00:19:33,559
Hey!

522
00:19:34,119 --> 00:19:35,440
I'm talking to you.

523
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,400
Go tell the Crown Prince later

524
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,240
that I'm done with this job.

525
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,119
Let him find someone himself.

526
00:19:39,119 --> 00:19:39,839
Hey, hey, hey.

527
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,400
It's not that bad, is it?

528
00:19:42,359 --> 00:19:43,160
How about this:

529
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:45,200
I'll go drag the Crown Prince here

530
00:19:45,240 --> 00:19:46,240
and make him apologize to you.

531
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:46,960
How's that?

532
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,160
Not great.

533
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:54,039
Move aside.

534
00:19:54,119 --> 00:19:54,920
I won't.

535
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,160
And you can't leave either.

536
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,480
If you leave,

537
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,319
what am I supposed to do?

538
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,400
I mean,

539
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,039
if you go,

540
00:20:05,039 --> 00:20:06,319
how am I supposed to become Empress?

541
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,599
How can you be so inconsiderate?

542
00:20:12,279 --> 00:20:13,079
Halt!

543
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,759
Special Envoy, please come with us.

544
00:20:25,279 --> 00:20:26,079
Yun'er.

545
00:20:26,279 --> 00:20:28,079
You've been married for several years now.

546
00:20:29,359 --> 00:20:30,880
It's time you took a concubine.

547
00:20:31,359 --> 00:20:34,400
Protecting you is all I care about.

548
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,759
I have no interest in men.

549
00:20:37,599 --> 00:20:38,559
Oh, you...

550
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:41,279
As my personal bodyguard,

551
00:20:41,359 --> 00:20:43,200
how can you only marry one man?

552
00:20:43,759 --> 00:20:45,000
It's embarrassing to even mention.

553
00:20:47,599 --> 00:20:49,279
I really don't want to be distracted by concubines.

554
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,720
Please withdraw your order.

555
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,400
Guards!

556
00:20:52,559 --> 00:20:53,880
Bring them in.

557
00:21:00,559 --> 00:21:01,519
What do you want with us?

558
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:04,119
Zhi Hua asked me to give this to you.

559
00:21:05,480 --> 00:21:06,279
Let's go.

560
00:21:07,559 --> 00:21:08,680
Aren't you curious

561
00:21:08,839 --> 00:21:10,599
how we know Zhi Hua?

562
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:12,640
Don't you want to know who he really is?

563
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,440
I can't be bothered.

564
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,000
See them out.

565
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:17,799
I refuse.

566
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,119
What did you say?

567
00:21:23,359 --> 00:21:24,480
I said, I refuse.

568
00:21:26,359 --> 00:21:27,839
You dare say no to me?

569
00:21:28,119 --> 00:21:29,640
I said, I refuse.

570
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,079
I refuse, I refuse!

571
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,680
Seize him!

572
00:21:42,559 --> 00:21:42,759
Don't move!

573
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:45,920
Let her go.

574
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:46,839
This has nothing to do with her.

575
00:21:47,119 --> 00:21:49,079
When I say take it, you take it!

576
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:51,279
Okay, okay, I'll take it, I'll take it.

577
00:21:51,279 --> 00:21:51,799
Come on, come on.

578
00:21:51,799 --> 00:21:52,519
Give it here, give it.

579
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:53,000
Hand it over.

580
00:21:54,599 --> 00:21:55,039
Oh?

581
00:21:56,039 --> 00:21:58,519
You sound a bit impatient there.

582
00:21:59,160 --> 00:21:59,960
Sigh.

583
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:02,119
Honestly, I'm not impatient.

584
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:04,079
I just find you ridiculous.

585
00:22:05,359 --> 00:22:06,160
Yun'er.

586
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,319
You're short on concubines.

587
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:09,319
This man shall be your concubine.

588
00:22:12,119 --> 00:22:12,920
Oh.

589
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:14,640
Now I finally get it.

590
00:22:14,799 --> 00:22:17,000
Rongcheng isn't about women's rights at all.

591
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:19,000
You're the only one calling the shots.

592
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,559
Take him away.

593
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,559
If you let him escape,

594
00:22:21,559 --> 00:22:22,680
I'll hold you all responsible.

595
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:23,920
Yes, ma'am.

596
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:24,640
Qi Zhi!

597
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:25,440
It's fine.

598
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,240
I'm used to it.

599
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:27,440
Move.

600
00:22:31,039 --> 00:22:31,960
As for you,

601
00:22:33,279 --> 00:22:34,599
from now on, you'll stay with me.

602
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,480
Execute that Special Envoy.

603
00:22:41,359 --> 00:22:42,160
Hmph.

604
00:22:49,759 --> 00:22:51,160
I need to speak with the Special Envoy

605
00:22:51,279 --> 00:22:52,319
about important matters.

606
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,400
All of you,

607
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:54,200
leave us.

608
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:56,480
But...

609
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:57,599
You...

610
00:22:58,519 --> 00:23:01,359
Are you trying to eavesdrop on state secrets?

611
00:23:01,599 --> 00:23:02,559
The Princess Consort has ordered

612
00:23:02,839 --> 00:23:03,799
that before the wedding,

613
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,559
no one is allowed inside.

614
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,400
Even Your Highness

615
00:23:07,599 --> 00:23:08,480
cannot enter.

616
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,440
No, no, no.

617
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:12,720
This...

618
00:23:13,359 --> 00:23:14,160
Cut the nonsense.

619
00:23:14,319 --> 00:23:15,119
Get in there.

620
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:18,359
Qi Zhi.

621
00:23:23,359 --> 00:23:23,759
Thank you, Your Highness.

622
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:25,359
Thank you, Your Highness.

623
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:25,759
Are you all right?

624
00:23:25,759 --> 00:23:26,519
I can't get up.

625
00:23:26,599 --> 00:23:27,799
What on earth are you wearing?

626
00:23:28,119 --> 00:23:28,920
Does it look good?

627
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,200
Never mind that.

628
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,039
Let's talk once we're out.

629
00:23:31,319 --> 00:23:32,119
Wait, wait, wait.

630
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,559
How are you planning to get out?

631
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,759
Fight our way out!

632
00:23:34,759 --> 00:23:35,720
How many are out there?

633
00:23:36,079 --> 00:23:36,839
Three to five hundred.

634
00:23:36,839 --> 00:23:37,119
Fine, then.

635
00:23:37,119 --> 00:23:37,960
Just leave me here.

636
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:38,599
Come on!

637
00:23:38,599 --> 00:23:39,759
Get up, get up, get up.

638
00:23:40,039 --> 00:23:41,279
This is no time to play dead.

639
00:23:41,279 --> 00:23:41,720
Exactly.

640
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:42,519
Today, we

641
00:23:42,519 --> 00:23:43,839
must come up with a plan

642
00:23:43,839 --> 00:23:45,000
to stop this wedding.

643
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,160
I've been thinking for ages.

644
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,720
There's just no good plan.

645
00:23:48,039 --> 00:23:49,720
Still, we can't just watch

646
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:51,759
as you become someone's concubine.

647
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:52,880
It's no longer the time

648
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,759
when I can sway this matter.

649
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:57,519
I can't stand her high-and-mighty attitude.

650
00:23:57,799 --> 00:23:59,000
We should rally the people

651
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,160
and drag her down.

652
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:00,880
And then,

653
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:01,759
let her go sit on

654
00:24:01,759 --> 00:24:02,799
the cold bench.

655
00:24:03,799 --> 00:24:06,200
Your idea sounds totally unreliable,

656
00:24:08,279 --> 00:24:09,480
but it might just be

657
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,720
the only viable option.

658
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,519
And she's deeply unpopular with the people.

659
00:24:12,559 --> 00:24:13,279
Who knows,

660
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,440
it might actually work.

661
00:24:17,319 --> 00:24:18,119
Prince of Rong,

662
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,799
you know Rongcheng's situation best.

663
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,400
We have no time to waste.

664
00:24:22,559 --> 00:24:23,559
If we delay any longer,

665
00:24:24,079 --> 00:24:24,880
he's really going to

666
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:26,839
become your Princess Consort's concubine.

667
00:24:26,839 --> 00:24:27,599
Hmm.

668
00:24:29,519 --> 00:24:30,319
I agree.

669
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,279
Rongcheng

670
00:24:32,359 --> 00:24:33,720
has turned into what it is now

671
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,680
all because of me.

672
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:39,240
But I only have one request.

673
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,039
Whatever you do, don't

674
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:44,400
hit her.

675
00:24:46,559 --> 00:24:47,359
Zhi Hua,

676
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,160
Qi Zhi is in trouble.

677
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,279
You have to help him too.

678
00:24:49,279 --> 00:24:49,720
Yes,

679
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:50,519
I'm talking to you.

680
00:24:50,599 --> 00:24:51,599
We have to find a way

681
00:24:51,599 --> 00:24:53,039
to take Bandeng down.

682
00:24:55,279 --> 00:24:57,319
Your good friend's in trouble and you won't help?

683
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:00,200
Is this your so-called principle?

684
00:25:04,519 --> 00:25:05,480
Are you sick in the head?

685
00:25:06,119 --> 00:25:07,279
You're the sick one!

686
00:25:07,359 --> 00:25:08,759
Are you trying to choke me to death?

687
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:11,359
How was I supposed to know

688
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,480
you were choking?

689
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:15,519
Just now you said,

690
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,000
what about that chicken farmer?

691
00:25:17,200 --> 00:25:18,000
Oh!

692
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:21,559
Your chicken farmer's being taken by Bandeng as a concubine.

693
00:25:22,119 --> 00:25:22,920
What?

694
00:25:31,359 --> 00:25:32,920
Congratulations!

695
00:25:34,519 --> 00:25:35,640
Congratulations, congratulations!

696
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,200
Congratulations!

697
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,039
Yun'er,

698
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:15,200
today is your wedding day.

699
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,319
You must treat him well from now on.

700
00:26:22,519 --> 00:26:23,319
Guards!
